Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:22.21,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}又将抵达何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:24.70,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:31.80,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不论去何处 若没有爱 都无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:37.14,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 H-KL\fs62\fsp0}Will I see you again? {\r\blur4}在道路的交点
